WoWs: YOUR WORLD OF WARSHIPS API KEY
Botsorgapi: YOUR https://discordbots.org/ API KEY, Optional. Leave empty if you do not wish to post to this API.
bots_discord_pw: Your https://bots.discord.pw/ API KEY, Optional. Leave empty if you do not wish to post to this API.
enable_console_logging: Enable logs to STDERR. Vaild values are either true or false.
error_log: An interger of the error log channel id. Leave blank to disable.
colour: A hex colour code to use for embeds. Example: 1660A5
support: Your support server invite link, leave blank for none
music_path: A path to the directory that contains your default playlist. Leave blank if you don't want one.
